<p><b>Is there a universal ASL?</b> The question “is ASL universal?”, may be one of the most common ones on the matter. But the answer is no! It is estimated that there are between 138 and 300 different Sign Languages from all over the world! Apart from that, there are also other variations of these Sign Languages.</p>